Class AeProcessImplStateAttributeCounts

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage.AeProcessImplStateAttributeCounts
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeProcessImplStateAttributeCounts.AeFakeCounts, AeProcessImplStateAttributeCounts.AeRealCounts
public abstract class AeProcessImplStateAttributeCounts
extends java.lang.Object

Counts occurrences of attribute values used for persistence by attribute name. The counts can be used to determine which values should be default values in AeProcessImplStateAttributeDefaults.
